attributes.action: Create a new body to regulate landlord and freeholder service charges
attributes.additional_details: It should provide free support to people to challenge charges.
attributes.background: We want the Government to create a new body that is empowered to monitor and regulate private, council, and housing association service charges, and impose meaningful penalties for unfair, inaccurate, and unreasonable service charges.
